parameters: Phew, I made it in time...

Just in time. Hurry and get into the classroom,
Deewan.

So you're Koushin. I'm Melissa Pierini, the
homeroom teacher for Class 2-A.
I am in charge of the subject of Ritual Studies.

Once I give the signal, come in and I will
introduce you.

You just explained everything and left
unilaterally.
Is that what you call cool...

I heard from my roommate that you're a popular
teacher among the students.
Well, she was beautiful after all.
